  org.leedsment.studentresearch.jmx.web.impl.JMXSessionImplListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.EventListener, javax.servlet.http.HttpSessionAttributeListener, javax.servlet.http.HttpSessionBindingListener
public class JMXSessionImplListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.servlet.http.HttpSessionBindingListener, javax.servlet.http.HttpSessionAttributeListener

The sesssion Listener implemented to create MBeans for a usersessionHttpSession.

Since the framework implementation is based on model MBeans, the same value objects used by the application can be exposed to management interface

The value object is registered to JMX MBeanServer using GenericMBeanExporter

Author:
Joseph Aruja
